Use the  style file "our_plot_syle.txt" to generate publication quality plots.

Add the line plt.style.use('our_plot_style.txt') in your jupyter notebook or python code. 
Make sure you have the file "our_plot_syle.txt" in the same folder as your code.

Visit this github page for more: https://github.com/matplotlib/matplotlib/tree/v3.4.3

If you some useful tricks for generating beautiful plots, add here.

# figure dpi
figure.dpi = 300 or higher are the best for publicaton.
figure.dpi = 125 could be good for plots to be displayed on a webpage.

# matplotlibrc-template.txt has the list of configuration parameters.
